<lyrics>[V1]
 kẖdny tạny jwh ḥḍnk wạ̉ḥs byk

[V2]
 kẖdny jnb nbḍ qlbk wạ̉sẖwf ʿynyk

[V3]
 ạ̉nsy̱ nfsy ạ̉lqy̱ ḥbk ạ̉lqy ạ̉ṣl ṣwrty ʿndk

[V4]
 ạ̉lqy̱ kl ḍʿf qwẗ mạ byn ạ̹ydyk

[V5]
 kẖdny ḥṭ fy rwḥk rwḥy fyk

[V6]
 kẖdny ḥṭ fy fmk wạ̉lyq ʿlyk

[V7]
 ḥṭ hmsẗ mn kẖyạlk ḥṭ lmsẗ mn jmạlk

[V8]
 ḥṭ nsmẗ ḥb ḥyẗ wʿsẖrẗ lyk</lyrics>
